					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The VDP is vanilla MD stuff, no modifications.<br /><br />What happes is that nothing happens, the LCD controller that takes raw analog RGB + Csync does not support interlacing and new field goes on top of old like in non-interlaced scan. Result would be flickery but since the stock LCD is so slow all stuff blends together.</div>

					
