						<div class="postbody">I just realized that this 2x brightness is a big reason they had that warning about playing it on projection TVs, since those internally have CRTs which already run at a really high brightness compared to normal CRTs. It wasn't just that games show static images (score, or entire screen for puzzle games), it's that they were drawing each scanline twice as many times per second as an interlaced signal.</div>

